member.name: R:Project_SqlRDDClasses
member.summary:
Thsi classes in the X# SQL RDD are part of 2 namespaces below.
If you enable the "implicit namespace lookup" option in your project (the /ins commandline option) then you do not need to add USING statements in your code and you an use them like you would expect, because we have decorated the SQLRDD assembly with ImplicitNamespace Attributes.
